<section class="row justify-content-around mx-auto">
  <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-in">
    <article class="card hvr-glow">
      <img
        class="card-img-top"
        src="public/img/mexico-flag.jpg"
        alt="Card image cap"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="card-body">
        <h1 class="card-title display-6">Mexico 🌎</h1>
        <p class="card-text">
          <strong>Welcome to Mexico</strong>, land of traditions, colors and
          vibrant flavors! 🌮🌵 Located in the southern part of North America,
          Mexico is a country rich in history, culture and natural beauty.
        </p>
