        <h1 class="card-title display-6">Canada 🍁</h1>
        <p class="card-text">
          <strong>Come and get to know Canada</strong>, the land of diversity
          and natural beauty! Immerse yourself in a country of vast expanses,
          from the majestic mountains to the immense coasts. Discover its rich
          culture, where indigenous, French and British influences intertwine,
          along with a vibrant mix of immigrant cultures from around the world
